items.Title: Mooshikha vAhana Modhakha Hastha
items.Expand:
Mooshikha vAhana Modhakha Hastha
										+ ShamarakarNa vilambhitha SutrA
										+ vAmana roopa maheshwara putra
										+ vighna vinayaka deva Namastehe      ||1||

items.Title: Jaya Janaki RamaNa Jaya VibheshaNa SaraNa
items.Expand:
Jaya Janaki RamaNa Jaya VibheshaNa SaraNa 
 Jaya Sarooroha SaraNa Jaya Dheena KaruNa 
 
 Jaya Lokha SaranNya Jaya Bhaktha kArooNya 
 Jaya Dhivya lAvaNya Jaya Jaghath PuNiya                 ||Jaya Jaya||

items.Title: ManDArammoolE MaDanAbhirAmam
items.Expand:
ManDArammoolE MaDanAbhirAmam 
 BimbAdharA Pooritha VEnunAdam 
 
 Go GOpa GOpee Jana Madhya Samastham 
 GOpam BhajE GOkula PoorNa ChanDram  ||Jaya|| ||Jaya||

items.Title: SaraNu SaraNu Surendra Sannutha
items.Expand:
SaraNu SaraNu Surendra Sannutha 
 SaraNu Sree Sathi Vallabha 
 
 SaraNu RA(aa)kshasa GarvasamhAra 
  SaraNu Venkata NAyaka
